sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Lambda
    participant Apify
    participant CDN as Instagram CDN
    participant Gemini as Google Gemini

    Client->>Lambda: GET ?url=
    Lambda->>Apify: Scrape post
    Apify-->>Lambda: displayUrl + caption
    Lambda->>CDN: Fetch image
    CDN-->>Lambda: image bytes
    Lambda->>Gemini: Extract event data
    Gemini-->>Lambda: EventData
    Lambda-->>Client: EventData JSON